## CMake Build Infrastructure

### Location
CMake modules are in `_cmake/` directory:
- `HDLHelpers.cmake` - HDL source management functions
- `IcarusVerilog.cmake` - Icarus Verilog compilation functions
- `VUnitHelpers.cmake` - VUnit testbench support
- `vunit/vunit_defines.svh` - VUnit compatibility macros

### Building
```bash
mkdir build && cd build
cmake ..
make                          # Build all
make hdl_<module>             # Compile HDL module
make test_<name>              # Run specific test
make run_all_tests            # Run all tests
ctest                         # CTest integration
```

### Dependency Tracking
- Module dependencies tracked via `add_hdl_source(... DEPENDS ...)`
- Test dependencies tracked via `add_vunit_test(... DEPENDS ...)`
- Dependency list generated at `build/dependencies.txt`

